event log
Bottom section
Gantt chart
algorithm comparison table
simulation timeline
UI expectations
color-coded states
clear labels
smooth updates
readable charts and graphs
ability to pause and explain during demo

17. Database Content / Internal Data Models
Even if the system does not use a full external database, it should maintain structured internal data for:
